                },
                {
                    "_comment": "Clamped impaction ratio (slinn_collection_efficiency, src line 344): max(0, St-S*)/(max(0, St-S*) + 2/3). The max(0, ·) keeps safe_ratio non-negative so the downstream sqrt(safe_ratio) in E_imp_unscaled is real-valued, and makes safe_ratio exactly 0 when St ≤ S*.",
                    "lhs": "safe_ratio",
                    "rhs": {
                        "op": "/",
                        "args": [
                            {
                                "op": "max",
